# Summary of Commands

| Scan | Command |
|------|---------|
| Host Discovery | `nmap -sn <TARGET-IP>` |
| Full TCP Scan | `nmap -p- <TARGET-IP>` |
| Service Detection | `nmap -sV <TARGET-IP>` |
| Banner Grab | `nc <TARGET-IP> 80` / `curl -I http://<TARGET-IP>` |
| OS Detection | `sudo nmap -O <TARGET-IP>` |
| SYN Scan | `sudo nmap -sS <TARGET-IP>` |
| TCP Connect Scan | `nmap -sT <TARGET-IP>` |
| Fragmentation | `sudo nmap -f <TARGET-IP>` |
| Slow Timing | `sudo nmap -T2 <TARGET-IP>` |
